    "text_and_image_8FC9CY": {
      "type": "text-and-image",
      "disabled": true,
      "name": "t:sections.text-and-image.presets.image_with_text.name",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Een_ultra_realistische_8K_lifestyle-foto_van_twee_vrouwen_met_een_Canadees_uiterlijk_die_samen_staan_in_een_stijlvolle_gezellige_kledingboetiek_genaamd_Susan_Lily._De_moeder_ongeveer_b4158af4-7214-4352-8c43-9d26ceb10ea4.png",
        "image_mask": "none",
        "image2_mask": "none",
        "subtitle": "",
        "title": "NICE TO MEET YOU, WE ARE SUSAN & LILY",
        "text": "<p>✦ We are a small Canadese family brand founded by Susan, inspired by her daughter Lily.</p><p>✦ Since 2016 we’ve been creating timeless pieces with care and personal attention.</p><p>✦ Every order is handled thoughtfully and every customer means the world to us.<br/><br/>✦ This past year has been challenging, which is why we’re opening our Revival Sale a moment to reset, refresh our collections, and move forward with renewed strength. </p><p><em>Thank you for supporting us through every chapter of our journey.</em></p>",
        "button_label": "About Us",
        "button_link": "shopify://pages/about-us",
        "button_style": "secondary",
        "align_text": "left",
        "image_width": "50",
        "layout": "right",
        "divider": false,
        "top_padding": true,
        "bottom_padding": true,
        "lazyload_images": true
      }
    },
    "text_and_image_4raDML": {
      "type": "text-and-image",
      "name": "t:sections.text-and-image.presets.image_with_text.name",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Zonder_titel_1324_x_1204_px.png",
        "image_mask": "square",
        "image2_mask": "none",
        "subtitle": "",
        "title": "Susan & Lily’s Revival Sale",
        "text": "<p>This little boutique began as a dream my daughter Lily and I built together in Toronto.<br/><br/>Late nights, early mornings, and a shared love for creating something meaningful.</p><p>For many years, this shop has been our world.<br/><br/>But lately, we’ve felt the need to breathe new life into it, to refresh, refocus, and bring a little extra joy to the pieces we share.</p><p>That’s why we’re hosting our Revival Sale.<br/><br/>It’s not about giving up, it’s about celebrating what we’ve built and stepping into a vibrant next chapter together.</p><p>By supporting us today, you’re helping a mother and her daughter revive our dream and create space for what comes next.<br/><br/>Every order truly matters.</p><p>Thank you for being part of our story.<br/><br/>Susan & Lily ❤️</p>",
        "button_label": "",
        "button_link": "",
        "button_style": "primary",
        "align_text": "left",
        "image_width": "50",
        "layout": "right",
        "divider": true,
        "top_padding": false,
        "bottom_padding": true,
        "lazyload_images": true
      }
    },
    "ss_testimonial_12_fz7qFi": {
      "type": "ss-testimonial-12",
      "blocks": {
        "slide_g9XyAW": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "media_style": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/generated-image_32.webp",
            "video_url": "",
            "controls": false,
            "stars_count": 5,
            "text": "<p>This dress is perfect for warmer days. The fabric is light and breathable, and it feels very comfortable to wear. It also looks quite elegant, which I love. I’m very happy with it.</p>",
            "author": "<p><strong>Linda A.</strong><br/>2 hours ago</p>"
          }
        },
        "slide_b8BQVz": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "media_style": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1080_1.jpg",
            "video_url": "",
            "controls": false,
            "stars_count": 5,
            "text": "<p>I often struggle to find dresses that fit well, but this one surprised me. The shape is very flattering and it sits beautifully. It feels comfortable and looks stylish at the same time. Very pleased with this purchase.</p>",
            "author": "<p><strong>Carol M.</strong><br/>6 hours ago</p>"
          }
        },
        "slide_nwzrKw": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "media_style": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Ontwerp_zonder_titel_38.jpg",
            "video_url": "",
            "controls": false,
            "stars_count": 5,
            "text": "<p>I’m really happy with this dress. The fabric feels soft and lightweight and it sits very nicely on the body. It’s comfortable enough to wear all day but still looks elegant. Definitely a great purchase.</p>",
            "author": "<p><strong>Deborah T.</strong><br/>1 day ago</p>"
          }
        },
        "slide_MpfDFr": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "media_style": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1080_2.jpg",
            "video_url": "",
            "controls": false,
            "stars_count": 5,
            "text": "<p>I wasn’t sure at first, but once I tried it on I loved how it looked. The cut is very flattering and the material feels lovely. It’s the kind of dress you can wear anywhere. I’m very pleased with it.</p>",
            "author": "<p><strong>Barbara W.</strong><br/>3 days ago</p>"
          }
        },
        "slide_Ax7JUz": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "media_style": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/hf_20260301_210916_ea29aff7-1aa2-4aac-aa13-2b26255fb673.webp",
            "video_url": "",
            "controls": false,
            "stars_count": 5,
            "text": "<p>This dress is exactly what I was looking for. It’s light, comfortable and moves beautifully when walking. The fit is very nice without feeling tight. I’ll definitely be wearing it a lot this summer.</p>",
            "author": "<p><strong>Margaret C.</strong><br/>7 days  ago</p>"
          }
        },
        "slide_VgfemE": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "media_style": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/8_d623f20b-c4de-45c6-a17d-50b2fca865b5.webp",
            "video_url": "",
            "controls": false,
            "stars_count": 4,
            "text": "<p>I wore this dress the same evening and already received a few compliments. The fit is very nice and it moves beautifully when walking. It feels elegant but still very comfortable. Definitely a good purchase.</p>",
            "author": "<p><strong>Anna B.</strong><br/>2 months ago</p>"
          }
        },
        "slide_w3pnRk": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "media_style": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1080_3.jpg",
            "video_url": "",
            "controls": false,
            "stars_count": 5,
            "text": "<p>I wasn’t planning to buy a dress that day, but I’m glad I did. The fit is lovely and the material feels really nice. It’s comfortable and looks very flattering. I’m very happy with it.</p>",
            "author": "<p><strong>Susan D.<br/></strong>1 year ago</p>"
          }
        }
      },
